.TH LOOTSHEET-JOURNAL 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-journal \\- Post and reverse balanced journal entries
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet journal [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet journal post --date YYYY-MM-DD --description TEXT --debit CODE:AMOUNT[:MEMO] --credit CODE:AMOUNT[:MEMO]
  lootsheet journal reverse --entry-id UUID --date YYYY-MM-DD [--description TEXT]

Subcommands:
  post     create a new balanced posted journal entry
  reverse  create an immutable reversing entry for a posted journal entry
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for journal
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet(1)
lootsheet-journal-post(1)
lootsheet-journal-reverse(1)
